description: Genesis our lightest speakers were designed to bring the best out of lower-quality music sources such as low-bitrate mp3 files youtube videos or old-fashioned analog equipment. These speakers enrich and restore sound quality from any musical source allowing you to experience high-quality sound regardless of the quality of your audio files. Combine genesis with your choice of mythband to create your perfect set of personalized headphones.
title: Myth Labs Genesis Headphones - Personalized Headphones - Passive Noise Canceling
